snippet.title: Everybody Wham Wham  - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Compete to build the best snowman, while making sure the other contestants lose. Out on January 29th 2021! Make sure to wishlist the game on Steam: http://s.team/a/1510630 

Welcome all, to the announcement trailer of the new Bonte Avond game 'Everybody Wham Wham'! Build, decorate and sabotage your way to the grand prize! Oh and did we mention that the game is filled with indie music and lots of characters to hang out with?

Follow Bonte Avond on our social media to get regular updates!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/BonteAvond
Discord: https://discord.gg/bU7GywxDxY
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bonte_avond

#BonteAvond #EverybodyWhamWham #IndieGame #Game #Snowman #Steam
